Don Galaor and Florestan, who waited for them without, seeing that they tarried, besought Ysanjo, the Governor, to shew them the Forbidden Chamber, and he led them towards the perrons.
Sir brother, said Florestan, what will you do?
Nothing, replied Galaor: I have no mind to meddle with enchantments.
