Come what will, quoth he, I will do it, to prove that you, who are the fairest Lady in the world, have the best Knight for your servant.
So he took his leave, and with rich arms and ten Squires passed over into Great Britain, and went directly to where King Lisuarte was, who seeing him so accompanied thought him to be some great personage, and courteously welcomed him.
