âI am; and I am he who will do to him and his all the evil in my power.
âAnd who are you?
âMy name is Don Quadragante.
âCertes, Don Quadragante, notwithstanding your high lineage, and your great prowess in arms, this is great folly in you to defy the best King in the world!
they who undertake more than they can effect, are rather rash than hardy.
